{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/PLOTWIST.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plot Twist</strong> immerses you in the world of the literary industry, where <strong>you can rise</strong> from an unknown writer to a <strong>chart-topping phenomenon</strong>. It blends classic tycoon elements with original mini-games, helping you handle every creative and managerial \u201cplot twist\u201d along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_BUILD.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/Plot_Twist_CAMERA_2025-01-04-11-05-23_1.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Start small, but as your success grows, establish a thriving literary studio. Hire editors, illustrators, and marketing specialists to help you reach new heights. Eventually, you can even become a <strong>publisher</strong> and decide what gets released\u2014both your own works and other authors\u2019 manuscripts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_UNLEASH.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/Plot_Twist_CAMERA_2025-01-04-11-05-23_2.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dare to experiment with <strong>various genres</strong>\u2014try gripping sci-fi, moving romance, or a mysterious thriller. You can also create books in multiple formats (print, e-book, or audiobook) and expand your audience to capture the hearts of different reader groups.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_PATH.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/Plot_Twist_CAMERA_2025-01-04-11-05-23_3__1_.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">While writing, you\u2019ll enter the unique <strong>Focus Screen mode</strong>, where you choose what aspect of your work to emphasize\u2014deep characters, thrilling twists, or captivating settings. Making the right calls opens up new possibilities and exciting add-ons for your final masterpiece.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_PUBLISHER.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick the right <strong>publisher</strong> or gradually become a publisher yourself. After each release, pay close attention to reviews\u2014feedback from critics and fans will help you refine your work and transform good books into true literary <strong>masterpieces</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_MINIGAMES.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/Plot_Twist_CAMERA_2025-01-04-11-05-23_4.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plot Twist</strong> not only boosts your creativity but also offers entertaining mini-games to give you a break from constant writing. On top of that, you\u2019ll face various narrative challenges and unexpected events during writing and promotion, bringing new opportunities or hurdles to overcome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_GROW.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/Plot_Twist_CAMERA_2025-01-04-11-05-23_5.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">By consistently writing and releasing books, you\u2019ll unlock new abilities\u2014from captivating plot structuring to masterful prose and impactful marketing strategies. Keep evolving to stay ahead of the competition and secure your place among the literary elite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3217130/extras/ENG_TEAM.png?t=1738587995\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bring talented individuals into your studio\u2014editors, illustrators, and marketing pros\u2014to help elevate your work. Each team member has their strengths and weaknesses, and the right mix of experts can turn any manuscript into a true bestseller!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"First Chapter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3217130/2e1d44e466f87ec4a96c66207f7e0b85ca4a501a.jpg"},{"name":"Bestseller","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommu